com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.jsonFormatVisitors

接口 JsonFormatVisitorWrapper

  • 所有超级接口:
    JsonFormatVisitorWithSerializerProvider
    所有已知实现类:
    JsonFormatVisitorWrapper.Base

    public interface JsonFormatVisitorWrapper
extends JsonFormatVisitorWithSerializerProvider
    Interface for visitor callbacks, when type in question can be any of legal JSON types.

    In most cases it will make more sense to extend JsonFormatVisitorWrapper.Base instead of directly implementing this interface.

    • 嵌套类概要

      嵌套类 
      限定符和类型 接口和说明
      static class  JsonFormatVisitorWrapper.Base
      Empty "no-op" implementation of JsonFormatVisitorWrapper, suitable for sub-classing.
